data.title: Portland Oregon Zip Code List
data.meta_description: A list of all the zip codes and maps associated with Portland, OR - Multnomah County Oregon City of Portland zip code map
data.text: Portland, OR is a city located in Multnomah County, Oregon and has a land area of 263.90 square miles (683.50 km2). The water area for the city is 32.22 square miles or 83.45 km2. There are 60 total unique zip codes in Portland, Oregon. The area code(s) for Portland is 503/971.
